ReportBundle.ReportXML: <Report ReportGID="c14b9268-7b07-4892-81af-cf8dd3be6b04" ReportUseType="2" ReportType="5" ReportName="Mixing Errors" Description="Shows ingredient mixing errors over 100lbs" CreatedDT="2012-07-09T13:18:07" ModifiedDT="2014-05-19T17:09:22.81" ModifiedBy="VAS" ConcurrencyTS="AAAAAAAAK7A=" ReportVersion="1" />

ReportQuery.ReportQueryText: <QueryBundle> <QueryText>select * from ( select hii.InventoryItemName as 'Ingredient' ,cmp.CompanyName ,dbo.GetLoadDescription(mi.FeedingScheduleMixGID) as 'LoadDescription' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.TargetUnitQuantity, 54) as 'TargetAFLbs' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity, 54) as 'AFLbs' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity - it.TargetUnitQuantity, 54) as 'AFLbsError' ,ABS(dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity - it.TargetUnitQuantity, 54)) as 'TargetAFLbsABSError' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(isnull((it.UnitQuantity - it.TargetUnitQuantity) / nullif(it.TargetUnitQuantity, 0), 0), 54) as 'TargetAFErrorPct' ,ABS(dbo.GetMeasurementValue(isnull((it.UnitQuantity - it.TargetUnitQuantity) / nullif(it.TargetUnitQuantity, 0), 0), 54)) as 'TargetAFABSErrorPct' ,CONVERT(date, dbo.GetInventoryTransactionReportDT(it.InventoryTransactionGID)) as 'ReportDate' ,CONVERT(time(0) ,it.TransactionDT) as 'StartTime' ,u.UserID as 'UserName' from FeedingScheduleMixInstruction mi join InventoryTransaction it on it.TransactionSourceGID = mi.FeedingScheduleMixInstructionGID join InventoryItem ii on ii.InventoryItemGID = it.InventoryItemGID join Company cmp on cmp.CompanyGID = ii.CompanyGID join HistoryInventoryItem hii on hii.HistoryInventoryItemGID = it.HistoryInventoryItemGID left join [User] u on u.UserGID = mi.ByUserGID) z where (1=1)</QueryText> <PreQueryText /> </QueryBundle>
ReportQuery.SQLStatement:
select * from ( select hii.InventoryItemName as 'Ingredient' ,dbo.GetLoadDescription(mi.FeedingScheduleMixGID) as 'LoadDescription' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(mi.TargetAFOz, 54) as 'TargetAFLbs' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity, 54) as 'AFLbs' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity - mi.TargetAFOz, 54) as 'AFLbsError' ,ABS(dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity - mi.TargetAFOz, 54)) as 'TargetAFLbsABSError' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(isnull((it.UnitQuantity - mi.TargetAFOz) / nullif(mi.TargetAFOz, 0), 0), 54) as 'TargetAFErrorPct' ,ABS(dbo.GetMeasurementValue(isnull((it.UnitQuantity - mi.TargetAFOz) / nullif(mi.TargetAFOz, 0), 0), 54)) as 'TargetAFABSErrorPct' ,CONVERT(date, dbo.GetInventoryTransactionReportDT(it.InventoryTransactionGID)) as 'ReportDate' ,CONVERT(time ,it.TransactionDT) as 'StartTime' ,u.UserID as 'UserName' from FeedingScheduleMixInstruction mi join InventoryTransaction it on it.TransactionSourceGID = mi.FeedingScheduleMixInstructionGID join HistoryInventoryItem hii on hii.HistoryInventoryItemGID = it.HistoryInventoryItemGID left join [User] u on u.UserGID = mi.ByUserGID) z
where (1=1)
